Class BlockMasks

java.lang.Object
dev.strwbry.eventhorizon.events.utility.fawe.BlockMasks
public class BlockMasks extends Object
Constructs a new BlockMasks instance and initializes all block collections. This includes ground blocks, non-replaceable blocks, and air blocks.
